tip.text: Sushi is pretty good, Dumplings (jiaozi & xiaolongbao) are just ok. Pastry is a little thick and filling too dry. Soup was also just ok but homemade noodles were very good!
Schönes Café leckerer Kaffee!
Burger gut aaaaber ... der Funky Schäufele Burger ist ein Oberknaller!

Salmorejo - a cold, creamy tomato & garlic soup. Great for lunch!

It is very smokey and smells really bad like a burger diner. (Your clothes and hair will too) The Air condition isn't working right. Food is great though - bummer!
Horrible - and I'm usually very relaxed when it comes to bad food. Had "homemade dim sum" which were MICROWAVED frozen ones!!! Service bad, Tip was included :-(
I liked the Caesars salad a lot but the gamberetti pizza was just ok. Frozen hurricane was pretty weak. Friendly service though.
